  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/2015_hero/public/2024-07/Header_Lattice_QCD_in_60_seconds.jpg?itok=73Tnc3Kt" width="1600" height="900" alt="Conceptual illustration of a pie with a lattice crust" />





